description:
George Noory and actor Bryan Dattilo from the long running soap opera "Days Of Our Lives" discuss his frightening encounter with several small childlike aliens, and how his mother had a dream of his meeting the same night it happened, plus whether younger UFO researchers will force the government to disclose the existence of aliens.
